. quietly mestreg education njobs prestige i.female || birthyear: || id:, distribution(weibull) nohr

. stdmestm Sm, reat(-.4603618) reatse(.1427249) reatref(0.0) reatrefse(0.0) varmarg(.8728384) timevar(tv) contrast

